summary: An ambitious Frontend Developer with experience delivering an immersive and attractive user experience through efficient web development, relentless debugging, and feature optimization. I am highly skilled in adaptive and cross-browser web design, creating functional APIs, and finding solutions for challenging tasks. Every time I try to learn something new, I take different online courses and watch YouTube tutorials. I am a fast learner, trustworthy, hardworking, and don't lack a sense of humor. Welcome!
